Revision history for Perl extension HTML-HTMLDoc

{{$NEXT}}

0.18.1 2020-08-11T17:00:22Z

   - Fix for doctype test failing on CentOS/Fedora, FreeBSD and older Ubuntu.

0.17 2020-08-03T19:16:07Z

    - Make all tests work with tests for new functions.

0.16 2020-03-10T19:31:24Z

    - get_htmldoc_command() method to retrieve 'htmldoc' command equivalent to your options
    - tweaks to the documentation

0.15 2020-02-15T03:46:14Z

    - Corrected misnamed subroutine (get_letterhead)

0.14 2020-02-15T03:20:50Z

    - Support for 'letterhead' option in HTMLDOC 1.9.8

0.12 2020-02-13T04:22:15Z

    - Support for 'u' option in header and footer, and the 'L' option for header.  
    - Added 'binpath' attribute to new(), to support alternate installs of HTMLDOC.
    - Method to set options for duplex, textfont, and pagelayout
    - Remove some unsupported options

